locality: Bordure de vestige de forêt primaire Andramasina (dt. Ambatolampy), environs de Tananarive.

55 KM NE of Morondava via route 8 at the forestry concession of the Centre de Formation Professional Forestière (CFPF), Kirindy Forest. 1.5 KM E of route 8 along principal concession road (Piste CONOCO) along S boundary to forestry block CN2. Roadside disturbed dry forest. Collected with D.K. Harder, E.A. Rakotobe, T.G. Razafindrabeaza & J.P. Abraham.
Est de Fianarantsoa, Parc National de Ranomafana, Parcelle II.
